LogicalColumn.Description: Ranges based on Days Until Expiry Date

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL OR "%1" <= VALUEOF("%2") THEN 'N/A' WHEN "%1" <= 7 THEN 'A: 1-7' WHEN "%1" <= 14 THEN 'B: 8-14' WHEN "%1" <= 28 THEN 'C: 15-28' WHEN "%1" <= 56 THEN 'D: 29-56' ELSE '57+' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" <= VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT") THEN 'N/A' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" <= 7 THEN 'A: 1-7' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" <= 14 THEN 'B: 8-14' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" <= 28 THEN 'C: 15-28' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Revenue"."Days Until Expiry Date" <= 56 THEN 'D: 29-56' ELSE '57+' END
